kida1985" id="mwA_Q">Sekida 1985</a>, p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwA_U"> </span>251.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-FOOTNOTEMcMahan2008-50" id="cite_note-FOOTNOTEMcMahan2008-50"><a href="./Prayer#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEMcMahan2008_50-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-FOOTNOTEMcMahan2008-50" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Prayer#CITEREFMcMahan2008" id="mwA_Y">McMahan 2008</a>.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-FOOTNOTESharf1995-B-52" id="cite_note-FOOTNOTESharf1995-B-52"><span rel="mw:referencedBy"><a href="./Prayer#cite_ref-FOOTNOTESharf1995-B_52-0"><span class="mw-linkback-text">1 </span></a><a href="./Prayer#cite_ref-FOOTNOTESharf1995-B_52-1"><span class="mw-linkback-text">2 </span></a></span> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-FOOTNOTESharf1995-B-52" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Prayer#CITEREFSharf1995-B" id="mwA_c">Sharf <span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwA_g">&amp;</span> 1995-B</a>.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-FOOTNOTEMohr2000282–86-53" id="cite_note-FOOTNOTEMohr2000282–86-53"><a href="./Prayer#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEMohr2000282–86_53-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-FOOTNOTEMohr2000282–86-53" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Prayer#CITEREFMohr2000" id="mwA_k">Mohr 2000</a>, pp.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwA_o"> </span>282–86.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-FOOTNOTELow200612-54" id="cite_note-FOOTNOTELow200612-54"><a href="./Prayer#cite_ref-FOOTNOTELow200612_54-0" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-FOOTNOTELow200612-54" class="mw-reference-text"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Prayer#CITEREFLow2006" id="mwA_s">Low 2006</a>, p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwA_w"> </span>12.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-FOOTNOTESharf1995-C1-55" id="cite_note-FOOTNOTESharf1995-C1-55"><a href=